There are certain people who leave a profound impact on your life from the moment you meet them. Bob Ingram was one of them. Years ago I met Bob and the Ingram family at the Porsche event during Car Week. Bob instantly took me in as one of his own, and since then my love and admiration for the entire Ingram family has continued to grow. Jeanie and Bob always welcomed with a big hug, and Cam became a brother to me. A legend and leader in Porsche collecting, a titan of industry, but most importantly a family man. We’ve spent amazing time together as families at various car events and adventures - and Bob lit up every room and lead every laugh. My love is with the Ingram family and everyone who was lucky enough to call him a friend.
